        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>A flowing cloak of utter darkness drapes over you, filled with pinpricks of light like distant stars. It imparts the stillness of the cosmos to you, granting you a +2 status bonus to Stealth checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Hide]{Hide} and @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Sneak]{Sneak}.</p>\n<p>While outside under a starry night sky, you're also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Invisible]{Invisible} as long as you remain still. When moving under a starry night sky, you are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed} instead.</p>\n<p>Gazing too closely into the stars is disorienting. Any creature that ends its turn adjacent to you must attempt a Will save; this is a mental, visual effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong>: The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong>: The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dazzled]{Dazzled} until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused} and Dazzled until the end of its next turn.</p>"
        },
